@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333
@serviceId = 050eaad5-68d0-4bfa-9962-d8bf22b29ed2
@serviceIdInexistente = 050eaad5-1g44-4bfa-9962-d8bf22b29ed2

### [SUCESSO] Criar agendamento válido para serviço ativo
# Esperado: 201 com objeto do agendamento criado e status scheduled
# Efeito colateral: dois e-mails enviados via SMTP
#   - cliente (clientEmail): confirmação de agendamento
#   - prestador (provider.email): notificação de novo agendamento
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services/{{serviceId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-22",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "clientName": "Maria Souza",
  "clientEmail": "maria@email.com",
  "clientPhone": "+55 (11) 99999-1111",
  "notes": "Terceiro agendamento para teste de conflito"
}

###

### [FALHA] Serviço inexistente
# Esperado: 404 NotFoundError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services/{{serviceIdInexistente}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-15",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "clientName": "Maria Souza",
  "clientEmail": "maria@email.com",
  "clientPhone": "+55 (11) 99999-1111"
}

###

### [FALHA] Horário fora da disponibilidade do prestador
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services/{{serviceId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-15",
  "startTime": "06:00",
  "clientName": "Cliente Fora do Turno",
  "clientEmail": "fora@email.com",
  "clientPhone": "+55 (11) 99999-2222"
}

###

### [FALHA] Horário com conflito de agendamento
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services/{{serviceId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-15",
  "startTime": "09:15",
  "clientName": "Cliente em Conflito",
  "clientEmail": "conflito@email.com",
  "clientPhone": "+55 (11) 99999-3333"
}

###

### [FALHA] clientEmail inválido
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo clientEmail nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services/{{serviceId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-05-15",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "clientName": "Email Inválido",
  "clientEmail": "email-invalido",
  "clientPhone": "+55 (11) 99999-4444"
}

###

### [FALHA] Data inválida
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo appointmentDate nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services/{{serviceId}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentDate": "2026-13-40",
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "clientName": "Data Inválida",
  "clientEmail": "data@email.com",
  "clientPhone": "+55 (11) 99999-5555"
}

